					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks for reading it and giving me your thoughts, but I need to clear up a few things.</p> <p>You do not need to know any of the backstories to read this article, in fact, it's the first time these characters appeared at all—I wrote it like that. And the part where bond says &quot;fuck you&quot; does not mean the deal isn't done, it just means he doesn't want to do it, especially with Douglas. I'll make that clearer in the article.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
